
KEYBINDINGS
-----------

Q          - cycle mouse grab mode & fullscreen game
Esc        - quit
LClick     - interact
RClick     - focus
T          - toggle flashlight
Mouse      - rotational movement
W, A, S, D - translational movement
LShift     - sprint
LCtrl      - crouch
+          - increase look sense
-          - lower look sense
Y          - toggle noclip

